This works for me in WTP 1.5.1.

The line that would return null and cause the NPE is:

WebApp webApp = (WebApp) artifactEdit.getContentModelRoot();

This would suggest something odd happened during your project creation, and that the web app content root object cannot be retrieved from the project.  I do not see this problem in 1.5.1 with or without server targets.  If you have a reproducible scenario, please reopen.  Thanks.
